| Concern | `src/servers/freddie-ai/daemon.ts` | ASL-0006 worker pool |
|---|---|---|
| Spawn mode | **Detached** + `child.unref()` | **Attached** — parent supervises |
| Purpose | Launch-and-forget MCP server | Stream stdout events + manage lifecycle |
| IPC | None — just logs to file | Line-buffered JSON events |
| Lifetime of parent-child link | Parent CLI exits; child orphaned | Parent supervises child until shutdown |

The "consistency" argument was illusory — they're already different patterns. Different spawn APIs for different jobs is fine.

